		Fetching [ITEM_COUNT] Items... [FILTER]
	</panel.string>
	<panel.string name="ItemcountCompleted">
		[ITEM_COUNT] 物品 [FILTER]
	</panel.string>
	<text name="ItemcountText">
		物品：
